<plot>Carter, a desperate screenwriter, is fighting a terminal case of writer's block. His luck changes when he discovers a small peephole in his wall that gives him access to the next apartment, occupied by a beautiful actress. Carter becomes intoxicated with her lifestyle. But his inspiration soon turns to fear when he witnesses more and more bizarre events through the hole.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?427542</url></doc>
